# ❌ Common Mistakes

## ❌ Mistake 1

Using different variable names.

Wrong

```text
INPUT Number

IF Age >= 18
```

Correct

```text
INPUT Age

IF Age >= 18
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ❌ Mistake 2

Using only IF when both outcomes are needed.

Wrong

```text
IF Marks >= 35

OUTPUT "Pass"
```

Correct

```text
IF Marks >= 35

OUTPUT "Pass"

ELSE

OUTPUT "Fail"
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

## ❌ Mistake 3

Forgetting STOP.

Always end the pseudocode with:

```text
STOP
```

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

